ntitsmall">Public Beta Software Enables Intel-based Macs to Run Windows XP</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td class="con"><p align="justify"><strong>Wed, Aug 2, 2006 No Spam</strong>, No Download, No Install. Free Trial.<br>\r\n            Reasonable Spread is an online permission-based email marketing and newsletter management system.You can use Spread to send product updates and discount offers to your customers subscribed on newsletter on your web site or imported from existng customer database. It allows you to create and send any marketing materials to your customers with a simple user interface. Your marketing campaign can be effectively held for increasing sales with a low cost! You can also use Spread to send newsletter to different interest group, alumni, association members etc. Spread can be applied to recruitment, import existng applicants or asked web visitors to subscribe your job post newsletter so that you can send related job opening in the future. </p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Why do you need Spread?</strong></p>\r\n            <p align="justify">Web-based System: No Download, No Install<br>\r\n              - It can be accessed from any computer connected to the Internet.</p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Email is popular</strong><br>\r\n              - Email is consistently rated as the most popular and most used application on the internet.<br>\r\n            - It is the preferred primary means of business communication.</p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Easy and quick to create newsletter</strong><br>\r\n            - All you need to do is just following the step-by-step instructions and typing the content into the template.</p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Saving time and money</strong><br>\r\n              - No creating, printing and postage cost of marketing materials.<br>\r\n            - Save your time by instantly delivering the newsletter or promotional materials.</p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Personalization and targeting customers</strong><br>\r\n              - Email allows your message to be personalized. <br>\r\n            - You can easily segment your customer lists so that your promotions go to the individuals most likely to respond to your offer.</p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Effective in increasing sales</strong><br>\r\n            - You can proactively keep contact with your existing customers instead of passively waiting for them to return to your website or store. </p>\r\n            <p align="justify"><strong>Extend your brand</strong><br>\r\n              - Newsletter can periodically provide the latest product information to customers. <br>\r\n              - It can capture the attention of visitors and strengthen the connection between your company and customers.<br>\r\n          </p></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td class="owner">east group, alumni, association members etc. Spread can be applied to recruitment, import existng applicants or asked web visitors to subscribe your job post newsletter so that you can send related job opening in the future. Inc. Other names may be trademarks of their respective owner.<br></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td class="owner">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n      </table></td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'HLLnNE1398653628.jpg', 1, 3, '28/04/14 10:53:48'),
